notes.text: This advisory aggregates security fixes for the samba SRPM in CIQ LTS for Rocky Linux 8.6. It addresses 9 CVEs: CVE-2022-1615, CVE-2022-2127, CVE-2022-38023, CVE-2023-34966, CVE-2023-34967, and 4 more.
